option.name: notice

BBiCat is a toolbox that combines different Bi-Clustering and clustering techniques in it, which can be applied on a given dataset. This software is the modified version of the original BiCat Toolbox implemented at ETH Zurich by Simon Barkow, Eckart Zitzler, Stefan Bleuler, Amela Prelic and Don Frick.
